<servinfosub id = "AFRAP70A7226010001">
<title>
Dépose
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Déposer le panneau A/C automatique. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AFRAP70A7226009"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
